{"tid":1623883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣&口號   正義之師 : 不擄掠 不傷無辜","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T17:59:43.000Z","uid":105976,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"982d24ad091679b3ab6d7361363e05f4bee966e7","tid":1623883,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"琴日偷野似係藍絲C9 &amp; 南亞人  但對家一定會煲大<br />\n<br />\n文宣&amp; 現場手足要繼續維持正義之師既形像<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不擄掠 不傷無辜    <br />\n違者軍法處置 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考岳家軍<br />\n軍隊要有戰鬥力，必先嚴明軍紀，令行禁止。岳飛給岳家軍定下了一條鐵律：「凍死不拆屋 餓死不擄掠」。有士兵私拿百姓一縷麻來捆東西，被岳飛知道後，當即斬首。(古時有民眾支持都好緊要, 現時更要靠街坊各種支援)<br />\n<br />\n俾人清楚知道裝修完我地係唔會偷  唔會傷無辜<br />\n1. 咁先維持到我地戰鬥力<br />\n2. 外國先繼續撐<br />\n3. 8成民主繼續擴大<br />\n<br />\nbtw  新歌 不屈進行曲  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kPFf1TF8QNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkPFf1TF8QNo&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=5b3fbdf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kPFf1TF8QNo</a>"},{"pid":"2bd85ed39b1bea7b5bae3d42d9b019d98e75ec6d","tid":1623883,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a1276b5d865167e39b7d893bd951a06ca80a3e","tid":1623883,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n等願榮光上架again!!"},{"pid":"92caa77b6640d85c91d8a59e85814ac1df3e7ce2","tid":1623883,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2159bc851e9f1ac5b6710be27b06db77f329b8a","tid":1623883,"uid":187050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"偷野獅鳥"},{"pid":"63740ad4fccab6a60ffbcb90e72100b058b0b956","tid":1623883,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci